section.section:
The Review Board shall consist of the following members, each of whom shall represent one of the following State departments charged with responsibility for an aspect of the State aquaculture permitting process or oversight of permit compliance:
The Department of Natural Resources, to be represented by the Aquaculture Coordinator, who shall serve as chair;
One representative of the Department of the Environment, designated by the Secretary of the Environment;
One representative of the Department of Health and Mental Hygiene, designated by the Secretary of Health and Mental Hygiene; and
One representative of the Department of Agriculture, designated by the Secretary of Agriculture.
